snippet.title: What Child Is This 👦🏻 Performed by Harpist, Amber Burdick
snippet.description:
Help a girl out by subscribing to my YouTube Channel! Watch a video! Like a video!👍This will help me monetize my channel! 💕Thank you! 💕
- Amber Burdick

Become a Patron to Amber Harp on www.patreon.com Every little bit helps! https://www.patreon.com/user?u=23511224

❤️🎄❤️Click here to listen to my Christmas Harp Playlist! 🎵 https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL_K5eaf2Dirjb1p4-1rSU5adL4W9609Lc

Website: https://www.amberharp.com

Purchase CD: https://www.amberharp.com/cd-for-purchase.html

Instagram: @amberlisaburdick

What Child Is This 👦🏻 

This arrangement in Samuel Milligan’s “Medieval to Modern, Repertoire for the Troubadour,” evokes the sound/feeling/setting that is very similar to Ralph Von Williams’ “Fantasia on Greensleeves.” I really like it! ☺️

Doing the #25carolsofchristmas challenge🎄by @rachelharpist and @harpcolumn for all #practicalharpists Let the fun begin!
🤗
